<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Collection Invitation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #2563eb;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #2563eb;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #1d4ed8;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>ðŸ“š BetterDocs</h1>
        <h2>Collection Invitation</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h3>You've been invited to collaborate!</h3>
        
        <p>Hi there!</p>
        
        <p><strong>{{inviterName}}</strong> has invited you to join the collection <strong>"{{collectionName}}"</strong> on BetterDocs.</p>
        
        <p>You can now access and collaborate on documents in this collection. Click the button below to accept the invitation:</p>
        
        <center>
            <a href="{{inviteUrl}}" class="button">Accept Invitation</a>
        </center>
        
        <p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
        <p style="word-break: break-all; background: #e5e7eb; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px;">{{inviteUrl}}</p>
        
        <p><strong>Note:</strong> This invitation will expire in 7 days.</p>
        
        <p>If you don't have a BetterDocs account yet, you'll be prompted to create one when you accept the invitation.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>If you didn't expect this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        <p>Â© 2025 BetterDocs. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
